# Charity Events Management System

PROG2002 Assignment 2

A dynamic web application for managing and discovering charity events in your city.

Features
- Home Page: Display organization info and upcoming events
- Search Page: Filter events by category, location, and date
- Event Details: Comprehensive event information with fundraising progress
- Responsive Design: Works on desktop and mobile devices

Technology Stack
- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js
- Database: MySQL
- APIs: RESTful endpoints for data retrieval

